      "value": "<p>&gt;@UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.class-features.Item.On2ZrPJTe8FURsXY]{Operative Exploit}</p>\n<p>You can unravel the subtle strings of magic as they close in around you. Once per day, when you are affected by a hostile spell, you can attempt a dispel check using your operative level as your caster level. The DC is equal to 11 + the other spellcasterâ€™s caster level. If you succeed, the spell has no effect on you, but may still affect other targets. When you succeed at a dispel check, you can also spend 1 Resolve Point to render any number of allies within 30 feet of you unaffected by the spell. The spell is countered if no targets are affected. At 14th level, you can use this an additional time per day.</p>"
